15:05.880 --> 15:09.160
Because I'm only talking about the facts,
not hearsay.

15:20.880 --> 15:21.920
Pizza!

15:27.040 --> 15:28.240
See it?

15:29.200 --> 15:31.160
Is someone calling you, ma'am?

15:31.240 --> 15:33.520
Ma'am, tell me, do you want some cheese?

15:34.200 --> 15:35.080
Sit down!

15:39.440 --> 15:40.800
I didn't do shit.

15:43.320 --> 15:44.840
I have been crucified…

15:47.760 --> 15:49.280
for my investigations.

15:50.240 --> 15:54.440
Come on. I'll do the--
A lighter? Shall we light them all?

15:57.480 --> 16:02.240
We found out
and we knowingly have touched

16:02.320 --> 16:03.960
high-voltage wires,

16:05.360 --> 16:09.240
which might have burned
or even electrocuted us.

16:16.920 --> 16:18.720
Extortion is a do ut des.

16:19.440 --> 16:22.480
I give you something
if you give me something.

16:25.200 --> 16:30.800
Since they couldn't find any real crimes,
they used Mayor Lo Biundo.

16:33.040 --> 16:35.560
THE NEXT PROSECUTION WITNESS

16:35.640 --> 16:38.720
IS THE FORMER MAYOR OF PARTINICO,
SALVATORE LO BIUNDO

16:40.920 --> 16:45.160
Two people that Pino Maniaci
allegedly extorted are two mayors,

16:45.240 --> 16:47.640
De Luca, the former mayor of Borgetto,

16:47.720 --> 16:50.240
and Lo Biundo, the mayor of Partinico.

16:50.320 --> 16:51.880
This is legality!

16:51.960 --> 16:53.040
SEPTEMBER 2015

16:53.120 --> 16:54.720
Mr. Mayor,

16:54.800 --> 16:55.800
something stinks.

16:56.760 --> 16:58.120
It stinks.

17:00.360 --> 17:02.560
Don't look for the mayor of Partinico.

17:02.640 --> 17:03.720
You won't find him.

17:06.800 --> 17:08.920
He completely left the city to itself

17:09.440 --> 17:12.360
because he's flying high, very high,

17:12.880 --> 17:15.360
in Brussels, in Turin,

17:16.560 --> 17:18.640
to get away from the stink of Partinico.

17:22.600 --> 17:24.560
What the prosecution wants to show,

17:24.640 --> 17:27.920
from its point of view,
is that there's a Maniaci system,

17:28.000 --> 17:29.920
which is a system through which

17:30.440 --> 17:34.120
various public figures,
particularly local politicians…

17:34.200 --> 17:35.280
PINO MANIACI'S LAWYER

17:35.360 --> 17:37.880
…are publicly attacked
by Maniaci or Telejato,

17:37.960 --> 17:41.760
if they don't pay,
and war is waged against them.

17:43.720 --> 17:48.320
When Lo Biundo was called as a witness,
of course, we were anxious.

17:51.160 --> 17:55.240
Out of respect for the citizens
who voted for him, he should do one thing.

17:57.480 --> 17:58.520
Resign.

18:04.080 --> 18:08.960
NOVEMBER 2018

18:15.720 --> 18:17.280
