18:17.360 --> 18:20.000
that he was never extorted
by Pino Maniaci, for a start.

18:20.080 --> 18:21.200
Let's see what he said

18:21.280 --> 18:23.960
because you're dreaming about
what he'll say in court.

18:24.040 --> 18:25.440
Let's see what it says here.

18:25.520 --> 18:28.520
Perfect. I'll dream it,
and then we'll put it to the test.

18:28.600 --> 18:30.920
-We'll put my dream to the test.
-Yeah, let's see.

18:37.400 --> 18:39.800
"I handed money over out of fear."

18:40.320 --> 18:41.440
This is the extortion.

18:41.960 --> 18:44.320
"If I refused, Maniaci would broadcast

18:44.400 --> 18:47.080
extremely damaging reports
for me and my council--"

18:47.160 --> 18:48.000
Stop.

18:48.960 --> 18:50.120
We have a council--

18:50.200 --> 18:51.760
Yes, wait. Stop there.

18:52.480 --> 18:54.840
I'm just here to show his statements.

18:54.920 --> 18:56.840
Don't argue with me right now.

18:56.920 --> 18:59.680
No. Can't you see
that they make them write these things--

18:59.760 --> 19:01.640
Now we'll find out from Lo Biundo.

19:02.160 --> 19:03.320
Okay, perfect.

19:12.880 --> 19:15.480
MANIACI'S TRIAL
EXTORTION CHARGE

